name: Wondrous Glow
description: Laser Art - Made in LaserLewDude's closet. By LaserLewDude. Blue line in background are from 488nm laser through 33 degree line generator and 50 lines/mm diffration grating. RGB laser through glass (Lumia) refocused by glass ball makes the violet color splash. Red 638nm through generic starfield diffraction grating. Green beams are 505nm. Glass platforms are dielectric glass.
